Name: Cleaning The System
About the game: In this platformer, you are a stick with bumpers that needs to reach the end of the level. You must bounce, slide, swim, or whatever is needed to get there. Features Different Mechanics: Bouncing, Swimming, Sliding, Launching, Gliding, Floating Speedrunning: Race against other players' times to be the fastest Split-screen Multiplayer: Race against 3 other friends on the same screen Level Editor: Create and Play levels created by other players
